Description:
Great Location in Koonoomoo!
Plenty of space to enjoy on this one acre block at Koonoomoo! Four bedroom hardiboard home featuring kitchen with new electric stove, breakfast bar and plenty of cupboards. Spacious lounge with new carpet, wood heater and cooling air conditioner. Master bedroom has walk in robe and ensuite, and the other three bedrooms have ceiling fans and built in robes. Handy to The Big Strawberry, Koonoomoo Store and Cobram, Tocumwal and the Murray River only a short drive away.

Description:
MURRAY RIVER RETREAT – 70 ACRES – FANTASTIC LIFESTYLE PROPERTY.
A very unique & appealing property with Koalas & Kangaroos at your back door and the banks of the Murray river only a short walk away. Excellent 3 Br Bv residence with open plan living, bedrooms with BIR's, ceiling fans, ducted cooling, feature fire surround with cosy wood heater. Excellent shed space, 4 vehicle lock-up garage, machinery and storage sheds. Domestic bore, sprinkler systems and well fenced paddocks.
Enjoy the good life with all the space you need.

Description:
Golfers Paradise
Do you love your golf?.... This beautiful North facing home is one not to missWith four bedrooms, three with built in robes and two bathrooms The central hub of the home is made up of 12 foot ceilings, catching that winter sun and plenty of light. The sizeable open-plan living, dining and kitchen area which leads through to the rumpus room, providing loads of living space. The home boasts a massive walk-in pantry, 900ml gas free standing oven, dishwasher, Caesarstone benchtops, perfect for those who love to cook.
The standout feature is the undercover alfresco which connects directly to the kitchen, dining, creating the perfect blend of indoor and outdoor living. The master suite is cleverly separated from the other bedrooms and features a walk-in-robe and ensuite with double vanity.
The home also offers zoned ducted refrigerated cooling and heating to keep you comfortable all year round. A large double remote garage with internal access, automated zoned irrigation sprinkler system, large front fenced yard, room for you to build a 6 x 3 shed.
Phone today to book your inspection!

Description:
Outstanding Way of Life
This property is a rare find, with such a striking combination of characteristics.
It boasts 1km absolute water frontage to permanently flowing Murray River Annabranch and overlooks the Cobram Barooga Golf course. A unique 100 dozen bottle wine cellar is one of many features.
An expansive multi - purpose 50 sq residence is nestled amongst ancient red gum forest on 50 acres only minutes from Cobram-Barooga townships and Murray River beaches.
Includes a fishing hut with floating jetty, stables with a self - contained flat, 3 machinery sheds, inground heated pool, landscaped gardens and much more. If privacy and space is what you are after this will meet all your expectations.
The main residence also has a guest wing with 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a kitchen/living room and separate entrance which allows a great opportunity to generate substantial income from a boutique B&B enterprise.
Features of the property include:
Main Residence:
- Master bedroom with BIR, en-suite with spa bath
- Additional 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms
- Family dining room with wood and gas heater
- Formal dining room
- Sitting room with gas heater
- Kitchen with double electric oven, gas cooktop and dishwasher
- Enclosed garden room / entertainment room
- Courtyard
- In-ground pool 11m x 4.5m with heating
- Ducted vacuum system
- 2 Carports
Adjoining wing with separate access:
- Access to 2, 3 or 4 bedrooms
- Access to additional bathrooms
- Kitchen with electric stove.
- Living and dining room
- Carport
- Verandah
Shed 1 - Brick workshop / stable 11m x 18m with enclosed storage / saddle room
Concrete Floor and power, gas & water
1 Bedroom self-contained flat with double carport
Airconditioning and wood heater

Shed 3 - Fully enclosed machinery shed with concrete floor 6m x 12m
Water - 2 bores, fully automatic sprinkler system for garden, rain water tank and pump, stock and domestic water.
Power - 10kw Solar system opportunity to get off the grid

Description:
Golfer's Ultimate Dream Home
Golfer, bowler or nature lover this home is for you! This immaculate brick and tile home is situated in a quiet location backing onto Tocumwal Golf Course and Bowls Club. The view from the kitchen/dining, family room and master bedroom has manicured fairways and established native trees. Total serenity.
The living room has a vaulted ceiling and a hi-lite window over the double sliding doors opening onto the outdoor entertainment area. The kitchen is spacious with electric cooktop and oven, dishwasher, rangehood and a walk-in pantry. The master bedroom has an ensuite and walk-in robe. 3 bedrooms with built-in robes plus a study. 2.5 garage for the handyman with internal access.
Ducted evaporative cooling, split system and under slab heating maintain comfort all year round. Ducted vacuum system. The yard is fenced with an irrigation system and bore water.
This home has been built to the highest specifications and would suit the most fastidious homeowner.
An inspection will not disappoint!

Address: i 6 Fifth Avenue, Boomerang Way Tourist Park Tocumwal NSW 2714
Description:
Holiday Heaven
Tucked away in the Boomerang Way Tourist Park, this little beauty is bang for buck. Situated within short walking distance to town and Murray River, you will find this home perfect as a holiday getaway or opt to live permanently - 2 bedrooms with BIR's, bathroom with separate toilet. There's a large carport - long enough for 3 vehicles - car - boat - camper trailer if you wish. It also doubles as an secluded outdoor entertaining area for your holiday BBQ with friends and family. The Park offers all park facilities and in-ground pool, with fees being very reasonable. The town of Tocumwal has everything you need for everyday living so you can kick back and just enjoy this beautiful area and our very attractive and increasingly popular Murray River.
